                <span id="dsq-author-user-203">DaCLmanInLasVeg</span>
            </cite>
        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-203" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-203" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>I have been selling stuff for years on CL.  I get flagged all of the time.  However, a few years ago I discovered a system that works.  I have 5 CL accounts, all have unique gmail addresses with phone verification.  I post an ad one day, then delete.  I rotate my accounts.  Eventually my account gets shut down, But my ads rarely get enough flags to get removed.  I never let CL host my pictures, my phone number is a jpg. and I never allow emails.  I don&#8217;t put all kinds of key words either.  I have considered trying to sell my stuff on other sites, but CL is still the king.<br />
I figure if I get flagged, I deserve it.   There is no way for anyone from CL to stop me creating more accounts.  I change my IP every time I log into my account and clear my cookies too.  </p>
